  "text": "• Numerical methods: Iterative methods based on fixed point algorithms, which are commonly used in thermoacoustic stability analysis, do not seem to be robust in the vicinity of exceptional points. A contour-integration-based approach [CITATION_1] facilitates robust computations of the thermoacoustic spectrum.",
